Related: Source Title, ticket

Product Tickets represent the potential OUTPUTS of production,
while Source Titles represent the INPUTS of production.

Each earthChange Product Ticket is a semi-fungible claim over a *projected* quantity and quality of some good or service.

Most Product Tickets have a natural "Window of Validity" documented as an approximate start-time and end-time defined by the real limitations of production and storage.

Single Serving Example:
15 minutes of taxi service between 8am and 8pm.  Good until Dec 2099.  [[THIS SERVICE IS NOT YET OPERATIONAL(click here to add work or money toward this project)]]

Subscription Example:
1 pint per month of organic grade AA honey

24 hour stay in minimum 300 square foot 'studio' apartment with private shower, toilet, bed, kitchen.
